	<p pid="a.108.2/1">The following table shows the number of doctors working in the National Health Service in England, who qualified in a non-European Union country. Information relating to Scotland and Wales is the responsibility of the devolved administrations.</p>
	<p pid="a.108.2/2">In Northern Ireland, there are currently 370 non-European Union doctors in training.</p>
